A naughty student from KZN was caught bonking his teacher. It is reported that the incident happened at Stanger Secondary School. The 13 year old student is reported to have been in a sexual relationship with his English teacher.The matter surfaced when the two were filmed having intercourse in the Science Lab after the school had closed for the day. Some report that the student was filmed by his own friends who got too excited with the visuals and thought of capturing on camera, leading to the leak of the video.Police from Eshowe Police Station are handling the matter. They have reportedly arrested the woman and she will appear in court sometime this week for having an inappropriate relationship with her student, and also for having intercourse with a minor, which is considered statutory rape.&nbsp;&nbsp;